    // Q_d extends from cl-d to cr+d.
    // We need cl-d >= a and cr+d <= a+p-1 to fail (P still extends beyond Q_d).
    // I.e., we need cl-d > a or cr+d < a+p-1 to hold... actually we need a < cl-d or a+p-1 > cr+d.
    //
